  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city skyline silhouetted against a vibrant, fiery sunset over a large body of water. The sun is a brilliant orange orb, casting a golden path of light across the water towards the viewer. The city is comprised of numerous high-rise buildings, creating a dense urban landscape. In the foreground, the water shimmers with reflections of the setting sun and the city lights. A few small boats are visible on the water, adding to the serene atmosphere. The overall composition is one of expansive beauty and tranquility.",
